settings.cardCss:
#toRealTime {
        background-color: #4CAF50; /* Green background */
        border: none; /* Remove borders */
        color: white; /* White text */
        padding: 0px 10px; /* Reduced padding */
        text-align: center; /* Centered text */
        text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline */
        display: inline-block; /* Make the container inline */
        font-size: 16px; /* Smaller font size */
        margin: 4px 2px; /* Some margin */
        cursor: pointer; /* Pointer/hand icon */
        box-shadow: 0 9px #999; /* Add shadows */
        float: right; /* Align to the right */
        transform: translateY(-4px); /* Move the button up */
            width: 100%; /* Full width */
            transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease; /* Smooth transition */        
        }
        
        #toRealTime:hover {
                   box-shadow: 1px 1px 1px 1px yellow; /* Glowing effect */
        }
        
        #toRealTime:active {
        background-color: #3e8e41; /* Darker green background */
        box-shadow: 0 5px #666; /* Reduce shadow size */
        transform: translateY(-5px); /* Move the button down */
        }
